{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/recipes/3-2-1-mapo-tofu","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Mapo tofu is a Sichuanese dish - a spicy, thick sauce with minced pork served over cubes of silken tofu. You can garnish with a bunch of other stuff, but that's mapo tofu at its essence.</p>\n<p>Those who know me know that I cannot stand spicy at all, but this stuff is not really that spicy, despite how some Chinese restaurants make it.  I love it served over a bed of rice and think it's really comforting and easy to eat. I sort of equate it to having a nice bowl of warm stew.  BUT, on occasion, I do modify my mapo tofu to make it even less spicy...hence, me eating it like a bowl of warm stew.  That being said, the recipe I am giving today should be more of a \"normal level\" spiciness - meaning probably that there will be some heat, but you won't need to go and down a glass of milk right after either. </p>\n<h4 id=\"silken-tofu\"><a href=\"#silken-tofu\" aria-label=\"silken tofu permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Silken Tofu</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 674px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/68c8697296616cc19a77777a8c635f6e/f9294/104-1a.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.61721068249258%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 1a\" title=\"104 1a\" src=\"/static/68c8697296616cc19a77777a8c635f6e/f9294/104-1a.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/68c8697296616cc19a77777a8c635f6e/90185/104-1a.jpg 450w,\n/static/68c8697296616cc19a77777a8c635f6e/f9294/104-1a.jpg 674w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Like I alluded to, this dish is very easy to modify and very easy to make.  You can add as much or as little spice as you want. You can probably also put it together from start to finish in about 20 minutes, which I love. The hardest part is really getting all the ingredients together, and I have made it pretty easy by breaking down the ingredients into stages. From there it's a matter of mixing together the sauce in a cup, browning your meat, adding in your tofu, and mixing everything together.  Three - two - one, easy.</p>\n<h3 id=\"directions\"><a href=\"#directions\" aria-label=\"directions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Directions</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1-mix-all-the-ingredients-for-the-sauce-in-a-bowl-or-cup--set-aside\"><a href=\"#1-mix-all-the-ingredients-for-the-sauce-in-a-bowl-or-cup--set-aside\" aria-label=\"1 mix all the ingredients for the sauce in a bowl or cup  set aside permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Mix all the ingredients for the sauce in a bowl or cup.  Set aside.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 726px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/e27fbdbc54c35d16d14fdfc921ac83f9/4e1b0/104-2.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 2\" title=\"104 2\" src=\"/static/e27fbdbc54c35d16d14fdfc921ac83f9/4e1b0/104-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/e27fbdbc54c35d16d14fdfc921ac83f9/90185/104-2.jpg 450w,\n/static/e27fbdbc54c35d16d14fdfc921ac83f9/4e1b0/104-2.jpg 726w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"2-on-medium-heat-add-in-vegetable-and-sesame-oil--fry-garlic-ginger-and-scallions-for-about-a-minute\"><a href=\"#2-on-medium-heat-add-in-vegetable-and-sesame-oil--fry-garlic-ginger-and-scallions-for-about-a-minute\" aria-label=\"2 on medium heat add in vegetable and sesame oil  fry garlic ginger and scallions for about a minute permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. On medium heat, add in vegetable and sesame oil.  Fry garlic, ginger, and scallions for about a minute.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 674px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/831a4fd9aceba4e0d656b309bb5e1073/f9294/104-3.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.61721068249258%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 3\" title=\"104 3\" src=\"/static/831a4fd9aceba4e0d656b309bb5e1073/f9294/104-3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/831a4fd9aceba4e0d656b309bb5e1073/90185/104-3.jpg 450w,\n/static/831a4fd9aceba4e0d656b309bb5e1073/f9294/104-3.jpg 674w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"3-turn-heat-up-to-medium-high--add-in-ground-pork-and-cook-for-several-minutes-until-pork-is-done\"><a href=\"#3-turn-heat-up-to-medium-high--add-in-ground-pork-and-cook-for-several-minutes-until-pork-is-done\" aria-label=\"3 turn heat up to medium high  add in ground pork and cook for several minutes until pork is done permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Turn heat up to medium high.  Add in ground pork and cook for several minutes until pork is done.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 726px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8ce8feed6d51bc80d910d5d59a0d8960/4e1b0/104-4.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 4\" title=\"104 4\" src=\"/static/8ce8feed6d51bc80d910d5d59a0d8960/4e1b0/104-4.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/8ce8feed6d51bc80d910d5d59a0d8960/90185/104-4.jpg 450w,\n/static/8ce8feed6d51bc80d910d5d59a0d8960/4e1b0/104-4.jpg 726w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"3-add-in-tofu-and-gently-toss-to-mix\"><a href=\"#3-add-in-tofu-and-gently-toss-to-mix\" aria-label=\"3 add in tofu and gently toss to mix permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Add in tofu and gently toss to mix.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 674px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/37119b4ec362db7e3f83fca4e39676f0/f9294/104-5.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.61721068249258%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 5\" title=\"104 5\" src=\"/static/37119b4ec362db7e3f83fca4e39676f0/f9294/104-5.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/37119b4ec362db7e3f83fca4e39676f0/90185/104-5.jpg 450w,\n/static/37119b4ec362db7e3f83fca4e39676f0/f9294/104-5.jpg 674w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"4-finally-pour-in-sauce--bring-mixture-to-a-boil-until-sauce-thickens\"><a href=\"#4-finally-pour-in-sauce--bring-mixture-to-a-boil-until-sauce-thickens\" aria-label=\"4 finally pour in sauce  bring mixture to a boil until sauce thickens permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Finally, pour in sauce.  Bring mixture to a boil until sauce thickens.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 726px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/fbf294bcab24a88a3ef8e20ecb2495f3/4e1b0/104-6.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 6\" title=\"104 6\" src=\"/static/fbf294bcab24a88a3ef8e20ecb2495f3/4e1b0/104-6.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/fbf294bcab24a88a3ef8e20ecb2495f3/90185/104-6.jpg 450w,\n/static/fbf294bcab24a88a3ef8e20ecb2495f3/4e1b0/104-6.jpg 726w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"5-garnish-with-scallions-or-chilies\"><a href=\"#5-garnish-with-scallions-or-chilies\" aria-label=\"5 garnish with scallions or chilies permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Garnish with scallions or chilies.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 726px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/0a2a491bc61216c7805489221a1b1cc0/4e1b0/104-7.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"104 7\" title=\"104 7\" src=\"/static/0a2a491bc61216c7805489221a1b1cc0/4e1b0/104-7.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/0a2a491bc61216c7805489221a1b1cc0/90185/104-7.jpg 450w,\n/static/0a2a491bc61216c7805489221a1b1cc0/4e1b0/104-7.jpg 726w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<section class=\"recipe\">\n<p><strong>Ingredients</strong></p></section>\n<p>(Makes 4-6 servings)</p>\n<p>For Sauce:</p>\n<ul><li>1/2 cup water </li><li>1 tablespoon corn starch</li><li>1 tablespoon soy sauce</li><li>1 tablespoon black bean paste (or Korean fermented bean paste)</li><li>1-2 teaspoons chili bean paste</li><li>1 teaspoon sugar</li><li>1/2 teaspoon ground black pepper</li></ul>\n<p>For Pork:</p>\n<ul><li>1 teaspoon vegetable</li><li>1 tablespoon sesame oil</li><li>1 teaspoon garlic, minced</li><li>2 teaspoons ginger, minced</li><li>3 stalks scallions, minced</li><li>1/2 pound pork</li></ul>\n<p>Tofu:</p>\n<ul><li>14 ounce block of silken tofu, drained and cubed</li></ul></section>","timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"Mapo tofu is a Sichuanese dish - a spicy, thick sauce with minced pork served over cubes of silken tofu. You can garnish with a bunch of…","frontmatter":{"title":"3-2-1 Mapo Tofu","image":{"feature":{"publicURL":"/static/104-1-86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386/b17c1/104-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386/00e5e/104-1.jpg 200w,\n/static/86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386/1a903/104-1.jpg 400w,\n/static/86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386/b17c1/104-1.jpg 800w,\n/static/86c53fd9a0c9ccfbca4d13b5ec14b386/7b761/104-1.jpg 933w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"feature_video":null,"date":"2014-09-25","categories":["recipes"],"tags":["recipes","meats","mapo tofu","tofu"]},"fields":{"slug":"/recipes/3-2-1-mapo-tofu